One-level Decomposition | Decomposição de um nível¶

In [3]:
Copied! 
# Number of decompositions | Numero de decomposições
n = 1

# Type of wavelet | Tipo de wavelet
w = 'haar'

# Storing coefficients | Armazenando coeficientes
arr_rgb = []

for c in range(3):
    channel = ronaldinho[..., c]
    coeffs = pywt.wavedec2(channel, wavelet=w, level=n)

    # Normalizing coefficients (for visualization) | Normalizando coeficientes para visualização
    coeffs_norm = list(coeffs)
    coeffs_norm[0] /= np.abs(coeffs_norm[0]).max()
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        coeffs_norm[i] = tuple(
            d / np.abs(d).max() if np.abs(d).max() != 0 else d for d in coeffs_norm[i]
        )
    arr, coeff_slices = pywt.coeffs_to_array(coeffs_norm)
    arr_rgb.append(arr)
# Number of decompositions | Numero de decomposições n = 1 # Type of wavelet | Tipo de wavelet w = 'haar' # Storing coefficients | Armazenando coeficientes arr_rgb = [] for c in range(3): channel = ronaldinho[..., c] coeffs = pywt.wavedec2(channel, wavelet=w, level=n) # Normalizing coefficients (for visualization) | Normalizando coeficientes para visualização coeffs_norm = list(coeffs) coeffs_norm[0] /= np.abs(coeffs_norm[0]).max() for i in range(1, n + 1): coeffs_norm[i] = tuple( d / np.abs(d).max() if np.abs(d).max() != 0 else d for d in coeffs_norm[i] ) arr, coeff_slices = pywt.coeffs_to_array(coeffs_norm) arr_rgb.append(arr)

# Image Reconstruction | Reconstruindo imagem
arr_rgb = np.stack(arr_rgb, axis=-1)

# Visualizing image | Visualizando imagem
plt.figure(figsize=(16, 16))
plt.imshow(np.clip(arr_rgb, 0, 1))

plt.show()
# Image Reconstruction | Reconstruindo imagem arr_rgb = np.stack(arr_rgb, axis=-1) # Visualizing image | Visualizando imagem plt.figure(figsize=(16, 16)) plt.imshow(np.clip(arr_rgb, 0, 1)) plt.show()
